 liver suggested though because of the comments saying they were too livery! Onion gravy was really yummy, though I pureed it for the kids so it was nice and smooth. Served with mash pots and peas like in the photo! It went down a treat with my lot and it is so filling! I served 2 faggots each for myself and the kids and my hubbie had 3!
